{"tid":646210,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[屯門撚] 有唔少朋友話屯門好好 :)","createTime":"2018-04-28T20:57:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-04T06:29:17.000Z","uid":27857,"like":59,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"c7305477bdb782687aec21f3be4e0a9dd38ce456","tid":646210,"uid":27857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T20:57:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我屌你老母<br />\n<br />\n到底我哋係咪住緊同一個地方？屯門周街都係蝗／新移民，根本就淪陷晒<br />\n<br />\n市中心唔再話，周圍聽到嘅都係蝗語。我本身住碼頭嘅，商場都變晒領展&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n有人話屯門多美食，聽完真係得啖笑，龍門居箇邊係有幾間小食店幾好味，但我覺得都係吹大徂，而且你食得幾多餐？<br />\n<br />\n屯門人口老化得好勁（高過全港水平），行入啲屋邨幾乎聞到陣老人馟，身邊嘅朋友搬得嘅都搬晒，平時條街好似無後生仔女咁，中學小學都因為「普教中」講蝗語，都唔撚係香港人來嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外，屯門當區就業率唔高，而且無乜office工（畀你都唔開係山旯旮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ），啲人每日要搭成粒鐘車出市區返工，來回就差唔多三粒鐘，真係人都癲<br />\n<br />\n最後，本身蝴蝶灣都叫做可以J下，但近幾年空氣污染勁到爆（因為污糟嘢由珠江口吹西北風過來，都係唔想搵source），每逢返屋企都氣喘<br />\n<br />\n間唔中入來玩下咪開心囉，可以搵下「隱世美食」，打下卡話要搵牛牛&hellip;&hellip;長住？不了<br />\n<br />\n睇住由細長大嘅地方變到咁，真係有啲傷感&hellip;&hellip;我住緊大學宿舍，畢業都唔知點算好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"712d7713989e15420371174047d1b36c92864d1f","tid":646210,"uid":27857,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T20:58:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我知深夜開post係無人理&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n其實我都係9up下，我都唔知有咩可以做"},{"pid":"707ee4815d557455c50113857858160170328c0a","tid":646210,"uid":27857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T21:03:14.000Z","msg":"推多下瞓覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05ecbabee0cfb30e530b66f57afceb17bc9e4687","tid":646210,"uid":27857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T21:06:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94c858ee18bfaaa2f1203fed0e3290e2fabcd21c","tid":646210,"uid":162854,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T21:06:32.000Z","msg":"Agger又多蝗又多蝻又多mk又多賊<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屯門=垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13122aff43647ab7c57b9c264e14aab1eeb63d9e","tid":646210,"uid":36280,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T21:07:20.000Z","msg":"屯門公路真係攞命<br />\n返工放工遇著塞車真係恭喜哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n再遇著中途急屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f6b0917825d871bcb324a82f4eb86e52337983f","tid":646210,"uid":16425,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T21:07:50.000Z","msg":"屯門真心垃圾 蝴蝶灣算撚數 d 垃圾多撚到 ，食野寧願出元朗，市中心一堆廢老蝗蟲 ，商場更加係垃圾無野行 ，好？邊撚度好？有何妖呢條仆街就知屯門有幾撚多傻閪"},{"pid":"b308dcc98804e7cb0e0f6d1c0ab26621dee91f63","tid":646210,"uid":27857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T21:11:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係不要再說了&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"e88c187fcf7cfc3a7e1bd0032b9ff28519608b3d","tid":646210,"uid":27857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T05:23:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6def9fa7cea0501c78c892772b61460bccd0d725","tid":646210,"uid":36670,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T05:34:11.000Z","msg":"以前去過內河碼頭見工<br />\n屌，仲耐過我搭車出尖咀"},{"pid":"1004f9b522ed098ffe78a85892e7f57d827fcc73","tid":646210,"uid":129829,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T05:37:19.000Z","msg":"多蝗但起碼冇天水圍咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7031889932256c7bc86235657d2486fa3106a4f","tid":646210,"uid":27857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T15:12:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8b545c14e91f676997c0b15036c5a4ab90edb16","tid":646210,"uid":82192,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T15:16:24.000Z","msg":"垃圾市鎮<br />\n狗也不屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0196ed418f7fddefc094720abbd14d091a4c5cf0","tid":646210,"uid":35101,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T08:54:33.000Z","msg":"屯門 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0ac756d1c3710eb448a4c0f595c28744541541c","tid":646210,"uid":96535,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T09:00:32.000Z","msg":"住屯門 = 低賤過曱甴"},{"pid":"0dee3434b89fe0541d97335cc8b52cec857cbf55","tid":646210,"uid":178110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T02:30:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0b91f4214bcd287c6b28ed20435f20904bb59a65","tid":646210,"uid":182240,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T02:48:15.000Z","msg":"但置樂真心好住<br />\n咩都有 又多野食 又少蝗<br />\n重點係間東亞藥房係冇蝗會掃貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd17a4035e1b7dadd5418f07fd1af2c080e2cd70","tid":646210,"uid":93318,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T02:52:18.000Z","msg":"市中心真係玩完 碼頭還好小小"},{"pid":"057e075336b7b3581b16104ee0cad917f52a98a5","tid":646210,"uid":28052,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T02:59:36.000Z","msg":"除左係市中心/海天飲茶<br />\n好少喺屯門食嘢<br />\n唔方便就真由其住下路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4142f5d9844e4b9c67af4599ea3e04bbe6a90f58","tid":646210,"uid":3818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T03:01:20.000Z","msg":"住近山 空氣好清新 又有山行 不過你叫我住成世 真係咪撚玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"550fa9b3565c28a4f8f1d8cda453579bb809e345","tid":646210,"uid":120935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T03:09:37.000Z","msg":"平日放假出街9成9都係阿叔阿嬸老野"},{"pid":"cbd4d05181b4eeda5a7a20a35619660977791a37","tid":646210,"uid":175004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T03:12:55.000Z","msg":"市中心真係死緊...行都唔想行..."},{"pid":"3a3708303aa67f37a4d70159a9867da60ba6d851","tid":646210,"uid":27857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T21:41:11.000Z","msg":"有時覺得自己介意咁多好傻仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但對屯門真係好多回憶&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"341267e2a2a083acad717c0db7cd66f7c8d75bb0","tid":646210,"uid":23445,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T22:00:30.000Z","msg":"得罪講句,住係屯門既,9成都係廢柴<br />\n爛泥扶唔上柄"},{"pid":"208c31b2ed0d4fdb5dbdd22e17bc06943168be06","tid":646210,"uid":47590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T22:15:54.000Z","msg":"唔鍾意住屯門覺得去邊都唔方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}